{"tid":587520,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"IELTS reading","createTime":"2018-03-10T13:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T21:09:05.000Z","uid":161330,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5825de161f0635de821f2cf7a555fbc19274ca51","tid":587520,"uid":161330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"事關小弟報左6月尾考IELTS<br />\n依幾日都開始做mock test<br />\n發現reading part我點做都得5.5~6(約岩一半左右)<br />\n上網都睇左好多skills<br />\n<br />\n以下係我compile出黎既step<br />\n1)先睇題目(circle key words)<br />\n2)睇first sentence of each paragraph<br />\n3)heading類題目(例如10選5)，3個3個咁搵<br />\n4)係paragraph first sentence發現同key words相關既字就繼續睇落去搵proof<br />\n<br />\n目前遇到既bottleneck<br />\n1)rapidly read好易<br />\n2)好多字都唔識<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跪求各位overall 9既連登仔指教一下我reading part<br />\n例如係有咩skills...或者一啲source可以提供都得<br />\n<br />\n感激不盡"},{"pid":"f295c2886cc26886ac055891aa92a8de7e12fcff","tid":587520,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"做 mock 冇撚用<br />\n做 pp 好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係講到好多字唔識噉係你嘅 data base 唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下雜誌啦<br />\n睇到每篇得兩至三個字唔識就係你可以上戰場嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e63a3fd50d9a5f14197d2ca61b5082b947ae40","tid":587520,"uid":11809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"IELTS Reading 無乜技巧可言<br />\n<br />\n真係考你識幾多字<br />\n<br />\n可以操10set pp 練，再背吓vocab"},{"pid":"c4d4cab59d487a7af70c16048c12a8aca9a2a43b","tid":587520,"uid":161330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f295c2886cc26886ac055891aa92a8de7e12fcff","tid":587520,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"做 mock 冇撚用<br />\n做 pp 好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.g